quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  114,1,"Say, \"I seek refuge with the Lord of mankind"
  114,2,The King of mankind
  114,3,The God of mankind
  114,4,(I seek refuge) from the evil of the devil _ (the whispering tempter)
  114,5,The one who (breathes doubts and) whispers in the hearts of mankind
  114,6,Amongst the jinn and the human kind